00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,400
-What makes it easier to remember what you have learned.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:11,080
A good method is the ten -minute rule.

4
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:14,480
The key to remembering better is repetition.

5
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:18,520
Because without repetition, what we learned disappears fairly quickly.

6
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:22,720
And keep in mind that you have to repeat before you start to forget.

7
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:25,920
The first rehearsal event should thus come quickly-

8
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:28,960
- After the learning - already after ten minutes.

9
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:31,480
Otherwise, you will forget pretty quickly.

10
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:36,160
The next rehearsal will take place after a day and then after a week.

11
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:39,080
If you want to remember all your life you have to repeat again-

12
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:42,160
-After a month and then after six months.

13
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:47,360
