Flashcard is also easy to bring-

21
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:10,760
-So take the opportunity to interrogate yourself on the break or on the bus.

22
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:17,080
Another effective method for remembering is to use association.

23
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:21,000
Then you connect new knowledge with something that you associate them with.

24
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:24,480
It will make it easier to remember.

