As your home or maybe along the way to school.

34
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:04,480
Then you connect what you should learn with the different places-

35
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:07,560
-And creates an association.

36
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:11,600
When you then sit on the test, you can walk the walk in the head-

37
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:15,320
-And pick up the fact that is linked to the different places.

38
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:18,560
It is important that you follow the walk in the same order-

39
